<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">2024年4月24日下午，学校理事长陈方平等一行七人赴北京市360集团总部开展校企合作会谈，360数字安全集团副总裁卜思南等领导热情接待。此次调研旨在深化校企合作，推动产教融合，共同探索数字安全产业学院的建设与发展。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">校长庄力可、执行校长范红铭、常务副校长李旺根、副校长吴志勇、校长助理张明等校领导，360数字安全集团市场部高级总监毛鑫剑、市场部高级总监吴妙然、市场部总监兼ISC学院副院长秦江艳、市场部总监任超等领导参加活动。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-25%2013%3A04%3A53%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%201.png?Expires=2029381493&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=qmpFfm0xjkHSmHOc2daELOHu7lk%3D" width="650" height="366" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; color: black !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">校领导参观了360集团，了解了集团的发展历程、理念，以及在网络安全领域的前沿技术、应用案例、创新成果等。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-25%2013%3A05%3A22%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%202.png?Expires=2029381523&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=ChFkH4r4WnUqFkR5ZNOYJIlhDbI%3D" width="650" height="366" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; color: black !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;">在双方会谈环节，卜思南代表360集团对学校领导的到来表示热烈欢迎，并介绍了公司基本情况、特色等。吴妙然、秦江艳详细介绍了集团的市场与生态部业务。陈方平介绍了学校的办学历程、理念、特色和发展规划等，并就学校井冈山新校区（筹）共建360数字安全产业学院的设想和计划谈了意见。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;">学校高度重视与360集团的合作，希望通过共建产业学院，培养更多具有创新精神和实践能力的高素质人才，为数字安全产业的发展贡献力量。360数字安全集团卜思南等高度赞赏了学校的办学理念、特色等，表示将通过校企合作，全力支持产业学院的建设。双方就产教融合、人才培养、科研合作等方面进行了深入交流，并达成了多项共识。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-25%2013%3A05%3A46%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%203.png?Expires=2029381547&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=2wbpO7sqg9vFQeSCvm%2F45gHNhvU%3D" width="650" height="285" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; color: black !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;">最后，双方签署了座谈备忘录，同时举行了“江西软件职业技术大学产教融合实习实训教育基地”授牌仪式。这一仪式的举行，标志着双方合作开启了一个新的阶段，也为未来的合作奠定了坚实的基础。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10.5pt 0pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-25%2013%3A06%3A08%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%204.png?Expires=2029381568&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=ZoNKR0mQdGXH5EfcXeCodZ6aMyU%3D" width="650" height="366" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1);"/><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;">此次合作，为双方在数字安全领域的深入合作开启了新的篇章。双方共同推动数字安全产业学院的建设与发展，将为培养更多数字人才、推动行业进步做出积极贡献。相信在双方的共同努力下，数字安全产业学院的建设将取得良好成效，为推动我国数字安全产业的快速发展注入新的动力。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10.5pt 0pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-25%2013%3A06%3A23%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%205.png?Expires=2029381584&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=z8E4Clen8x8gop5syn2n5g9pnYs%3D" width="650" height="312" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1);"/></span></p><p><br/></p>